nodes.text: World of Reading Star Wars Boxed Set: Level 1

World of Reading Star Wars Boxed Set: Level 1 is a collection of six Star Wars young-reader books in the World of Reading Level 1 series. The included titles are Escape from Darth Vader, AT-AT Attack!, Ewoks Join the Fight, Finn and Poe Team Up!, BB-8 Finds a Friend, and Chaos at the Castle. The set was published by Disney–Lucasfilm Press on October 25, 2016.
